AUDIO: 'Well, it\'s another wild day of AI updates. Today, we\'ve got a new fast video model. Uh, maybe the fastest we\'ve seen yet. Uh, and it\'s cheap, but is it good? We\'ll find out today. Plus, the return of well, kind of a legendary name in AI video. One that I thought was lost'

